description:
Stuck on what to play or what to buy? Join TVGS as I list and discuss ten of the most over looked and obscure PSP hidden gems that deserve way more love and attention. Many lesser known games have released for the Playstation portable, so let me know your choice of the top 10 overlooked games on the handheld console down below!
